# Installation

Install Herold by following these steps.

## System requirements

Herold runs on Linux, macOS, and Windows.

## Download

Download the latest release from the official website at https://herold.dev.

## Configuration

Edit the configuration file.

{% include file="snippets/config.toml" lang="toml" /%}

## Keyboard shortcuts

Use {% kbd keys="Mod K" /%} to open command palette.
